#

Balsamic Glazed Brussels Sprouts and Bacon

$15.99
250 kcal

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbPaleo

Tags:

Vegetable DishSide DishComfort Food

Description

A savory side dish of caramelized Brussels sprouts with crispy bacon and a tangy balsamic glaze.

Ingredients

  • Brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • Bacon: 6 slices
  • Balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
